General.Name: Fujian Yuanxiang New Materials Co. Ltd. A
General.Description: Fujian Yuanxiang New Materials Co.,Ltd engages in the development, production, and sale of nano-silica products. Its products include silicone rubber YX-800 series, silicone rubber YX -1000 series, and matting agent M series. The company's products are used in the fields of silicone rubber; coating; insulation material; green tire; and other fields, such as additives. It serves customers through its sales network in China and internationally. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in Shaowu, China.
